#

Braised Short Ribs with Creamy Polenta and Roasted Brussels Sprouts

$35
1200 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinComfort Food

Tags:

BeefComfort FoodGourmetHearty

Description

Tender braised short ribs served over creamy polenta with a side of crispy roasted Brussels sprouts, a luxurious comfort dish.

Ingredients

  • Beef short ribs: 3 lbs
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Carrots: 2, diced
  • Onion: 1, chopped
  • Celery: 2 stalks, chopped
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Red wine: 2 cups
  • Beef broth: 4 cups
  • Thyme: 2 sprigs
  • Bay leaves: 2
  • Polenta: 1 cup
  • Heavy cream: 1 cup
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Brussels sprouts: 1 lb, halved
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
